        "action": "Make it compulsory for all schools to follow NHS guidelines on D&V Bugs.",
        "additional_details": "https://www.publichealth.hscni.net/sites/default/files/Guidance_on_infection_control_in%20schools_poster.pdf\r\n\r\nhttps://www.nhs.uk/conditions/diarrhoea-and-vomiting/",
        "background": "At present, all schools set their own policy regarding the length of time given for children to return to school after the d&v bug. According to nhs guidelines this should be 48hrs after the last d or v episode. Many schools are setting a 24hr policy resulting in an outbreak.",
